			<h4 class="light underline uppercase">About Our Guest House</h4>
      <p class="light">Located on the beachfront in Felidhoo, Magiclife Guesthouse features a shared lounge. Boasting a 24-hour front desk, this property also provides guests with a restaurant. The property offers a children's playground. At the guest house, every room comes with a wardrobe. The private bathroom is fitted with a shower. A continental or buffet breakfast is available daily at the property. Skiing is among the activities that guests can enjoy near Magiclife Guesthouse. We speak your language!</p>
    </div>
